DOCUMENTATION
=============

See https://rpc.ote.gandi.net/doc/2.0/

API endpoint:

* Test: https://rpc.ote.gandi.net/xmlrpc/
* Production: https://rpc.gandi.net/xmlrpc/

USAGE
=====

require 'gandi'

# test env
api = Gandi::Session.connect("24-character API key", "https://rpc.gandi.net/xmlrpc/")

api.domain.list
api.domain.info('mydomain.com')
...


# production env
api = Gandi::Session.connect("24-character API key")
api.domain.list
api.domain.info('mydomain.com')
...